
Syntax: d_isplay ma_iltext

Description: Shows you the status of your mail and the mailtext flag.
   If the mailtext flag is on, then when you issue a command to send
   mail, the standard mail program will be invoked.  If the mailtext
   flag is off, then Yapp will collect the text to be mailed to the 
   destination.

See also: mail, set mailtext
